# Create OIDC Connection - Stytch Docs
created: 2026-01-28, last updated: 2026-03-21, [Read more](https://stytch.com/docs/api-reference/b2b/api/sso/oidc/create-oidc-connection)

```
// POST /v1/b2b/sso/oidc/{organization_id}
const stytch = require('stytch');
const client = new stytch.B2BClient({
project_id: '${projectId}',
secret: '${secret}',
});
const params = {
organization_id: "${organizationId}",
display_name: "Example OIDC connection",
};
const options = {
authorization: {
session_token: '${sessionToken}',
},
};
client.SSO.OIDC.CreateConnection(params, options)
.then(resp => { console.log(resp) })
.catch(err => { console.log(err) });
```
